{"tid":1639283,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"交通安全 回帶 深井鐵蒺藜爆胎黨","createTime":"2019-10-08T14:44:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T04:22:07.000Z","uid":136860,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"dda26c1065151d3fc8def9bb9f5117aca97b364a","tid":1639283,"uid":136860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T14:44:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4nPBFo2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4nPBFo2.jpg&h=76183e29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【橙訊】青山公路近深井段和汀九橋附近路面，近日散布大量貌似忍者飛鏢的四爪釘「鐵蒺藜」，警方接獲5宗市民報案，至今聯絡上其中一名受害的駕駛者。<br />\n<br />\n警方新界北總區交通部警司曾憲健早上在電台節目中表示，警方接獲5宗同類舉報，指青山公路近深井段和汀九橋附近，有鐵釘散布路面。他強調警方關注事件，荃灣警區重案組已接手調查，暫列求警協助案處理。<br />\n<br />\n曾憲健估計，路面上的「鐵蒺藜」與換胎後被棄置，或與惡作劇有關。他警告有關行為危害車輛行駛安全，甚至釀成受傷，屬嚴重罪行，市民切勿以身試法。他呼籲市民若一旦發現，可致電警方999熱線，或新界北交通部電話36613800提供消息。<br />\n<br />\n他建議司機行車時，應保持於行車線，勿駛近路邊肩；萬一被「<span style=\"color: red;\">鐵蒺藜</span>」刺上而爆胎，司機應停於路邊，並亮起死火燈，一切以安全為上。對於有市民估計，事件或與深井一帶的嚴重飛車活動有關，曾憲健承認區內晚上有車輛高速行駛情況。<br />\n<br />\n來源：<a href=\"http://www.orangenews.hk/news/system/2019/01/04/010107135.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.orangenews.hk%2Fnews%2Fsystem%2F2019%2F01%2F04%2F010107135.shtml&d=cH2nQL%2B7gNVGRZzFZPB6Voc%2FDYnbIFO1z8NzTSvCTwQ%3D&h=7cc07c6e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.orangenews.hk/news/system/2019/01/04/010107135.shtml</a><br />\n<br />\n近排有好多罔顧交通安全高速行駛既司機出玩喺馬路上<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔排除會引黎深井爆胎黨出沒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n為左保障自己唔好踩釘建議大家買返對<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">鋼頭鋼底</span></span>既安全鞋<br />\n二三百蚊有對靚靚囝囝既 扔左都唔心痛<br />\n貴既仲可以防車爆腳趾<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但千祈唔好踢人</span></span> 返工比佢踢過好似斷骨咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無帶防具既頭真係唔好踢 真係會踢死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n交通零意外 香港人人愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"806aed23f6a56bf5e037cc217670797facd2c3b3","tid":1639283,"uid":136860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T14:57:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8f59f5438ffdbd56e2d8efa361a33fe3c66e87a9","tid":1639283,"uid":125542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T15:40:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b42e7888dcf9b879a2103ef412237e6dd7349a0","tid":1639283,"uid":47775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T15:41:51.000Z","msg":"放係狗屋門口"},{"pid":"d981c043d7a22a275c6c96f4ca203aa00229da9d","tid":1639283,"uid":258226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f59f5438ffdbd56e2d8efa361a33fe3c66e87a9","tid":1639283,"uid":125542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T15:40:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T15:49:50.000Z","msg":"去五金鋪買鐵釘，再買盒AB膠，自制"},{"pid":"440197b71904af480cdfe9a7122c7f2e78e96677","tid":1639283,"uid":136860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T23:28:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"126c8d791245e976405e8522ded3bb7b4e3cbe36","tid":1639283,"uid":136860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T04:22:07.000Z","msg":"推"}]}